      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be under version-controlled release with documented regression test suite covering relevant flow regimes.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under ISO 9001-compliant QMS. Regression test suite covers laminar, turbulent, and rotating-frame flow cases. Version control and release notes archived. Achieved level 2 confirmed."
    },
