      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published benchmarking studies for centrifugal blood pumps (Fraser et al. 2011, Hariharan et al. 2011). Model form uncertainty not formally quantified at MRL 2 but model selection is well-supported by domain literature."
